		"description": "<p>At 3rd level you gain proficiency with the Engineering skill. If you are already proficient with it, you instead gain proficiency with another skill from the scholar list. In addition, you gain an expertise die on all Engineering checks. At level 7 this increases to a d6, at level 10 it increases to a d8 and your maximum size for expertise die on Engineering increases to d10, and at level 14 increases to a d10 and your maximum size for expertise die on Engineering increases to d12. You may always choose to use Intelligence on Engineering checks.</p><p>You also add @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-feats.Item.fs2rwplugvwip86h]{Crossbow Expertise} to the list of bonus feats you may choose.</p>",
